description._content: Collection: NASA Marshall Space Flight Center Collection Name of Image: Fire Fighter's Attire Full Description: Marshall Space Flight Center used technology from astronauts' space suits to improve the safety of firefighter's attire. The new fire attire is lightweight, fire-resistant, and heat-protective.
